title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre likely to score unexpected results once you resurrect a regimen or discipline you tried in the past. The regenerative Scorpio New Moon falls in your 6th House of Daily Flow, prompting you to revive and reevaluate old practices. Perhaps you were unable to accept the demands of this routine before now, but a cosmic jolt might be strong enough for you to reconsider your previous conclusions. The novelty of the current moment catalyzes your interest and commitment. Surprising yourself, even in small ways, is one way to stay persistent. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
